attributes.summary: Machine Learning uses algorithms trained on data for prediction/decisions; key methods are neural networks, decision trees, support vector machines.
"Neural Networks use algorithms inspired by the human brain to identify patterns in sensory data, processing inputs via multiple layers (input, hidden, output) for classification or clustering."
"Deep Learning, using multi-layered neural networks, powers advancements in AI like computer vision and NLP." [Critical: natural language processing]
